<br>
In the case of a late notification or something, you're going to have some people who are run over by this policy that have patiently waited their turn to have their shot at Nagafen or Vox.  Plus, as we've seen most recently with Nagafen, they needed more than one shot on him...this could cause a problem where people are still learning about how to do things like Dragon raids and they get stiffed on their opportunity where they could have succeeded.<br>
<br>
If you grandfather everyone with a current Reservation to 48 hours, and then notify that the list has changed to 24 hours for all new reservations, that would be ok (you know it when you sign up), but would cause a lot more work for you Shao (like you didn't have enough already).  Maybe it'd keep you from getting a different colored BP every couple of months.  <br>
